<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.7.9">
<l>kāviyaṅ kaṇṇiyeṇṇil kaṭimāmalarp pāvaiyoppāḷ</l>
<l>pāviyēṉ peṟṟamaiyāl paṇaittōḷipa rakkaḻintu</l>
<l>tūvicē raṉṉamaṉṉa naṭaiyāḷneṭu māloṭumpōy</l>
<l>vāviyan taṇpaṇaicūḻ vayalālipu kuvarkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>If [I] put a value on the one with lily eyes, she is like the goddess</l>
<l rend="indent">on the great, fragrant blossom;</l>
<l>I [became] a wretch by begetting that bamboo-armed [girl]. Her body failing,</l>
<l>As she with a gait like a feathered swan’s goes with tall Māl,</l>
<l>Are they setting out for Āli with paddy fields encircled</l>
<l rend="indent">by cool tanks of stepwells?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
